tafsir[11]{c,v,t}:
  101,1,"Tuma nde ɓerɗe konngete saba mawnude kul huli."
  101,2,"Hol ko woni o waktu mbo ɓerɗe na konnge sabu mawnude kul huli?"
  101,3,"Hol ko anndin Ma-aan nelaaɗo-o waktu mbo ɓerɗe aade en ndillata sabu mawnude kulol hembo? Kombo ñande darnga."
  101,4,"ñande ɓerɗe aade en ndilli ɓe mba*a no mbeɗon Alla carikon caaktikon bannge yo bannge."
  101,5,"Pelle ɗee mba*a hono hottolo goobaako e hoyde yaadu mum e dille mum."
  101,6,"Tawi ko oon mbo golle mum moƴƴe ɓuri teddude golle mum bonɗe."
  101,7,"Hara hombo e nguurndam mbelɗam ɗam o heɓata ka aljanna."
  101,8,"Tawi ko oon mbo golle mum bonɗe ɓuri teddude e dow golle mum lobbe."
  101,9,"Hoɗorde makko e ñiiɓirde makko ñande darnga ko jahannama."
  101,10,"Hol ko anndin Ma-aan nelaaɗo-hol ko woni ngeen?."
  101,11,"Ko nge yiite wulnge jaw."
